latestIgtvVideos.title: Voltasbeko #iamenough #mothersday #dedicated to mothers
latestIgtvVideos.caption: How many of us feel the need to wear multiple hats to become the perfect mom we think we need to be? How many of us realize that we are enough? As this film beautifully shows, it could be something simple that your child says, that makes you believe, “Yes, I am enough!” Our film made in association with Voltas Beko is inspired by single moms and their strength and resilience, as they juggle multiple roles and face the greatest challenges everyday. What better way to celebrate Mother’s Day, than to extend this thought to every mother, to celebrate her and ask her to believe in this simple self-affirmation, #iamenough #iamenought @momspresso @voltasbeko

Happy Lohri to everyone &
Lohri is a popular Indian festival that is celebrated to mark the beginning of the harvest season for winter crops.
Singing folk songs, dancing to the tunes of dhol, performing bhangra and munching gajak, moongfali, tilkut, puffed rice, revdi, popcorn by the bonfire are some of the popular Lohri rituals.
